Syntax: rulers

Displays the current rulers and their affiliations in the game world.
Rulers are named characters who control areas or hold special titles
granted by the game's political system. Each ruler is listed with their
rank title, name, and the group or faction they are affiliated with.

Rulers may also control specific areas of the game world, which is listed
beneath their entry if applicable.

Ruler titles reflect rank and gender (e.g., King/Queen, Lord/Lady).

See also: politics clan clist
